{%- comment -%}
  ================================================================
  Wholesale lock status
  Single source of truth for the "wholesale-only" gating logic.

  Because `render` creates an isolated variable scope, this snippet
  works by OUTPUTTING a sentinel string. Callers capture the output
  and check whether it contains the relevant marker.

  Inputs (one of):
    - product:    product object to evaluate
    - collection: collection object to evaluate

  Output markers (any combination, space-separated):
    - "is-b2b"             customer has the 'B2B' tag
    - "product-locked"     product belongs to a wholesale-only collection
                           AND customer is not B2B
    - "collection-locked"  collection is a wholesale-only collection
                           AND customer is not B2B

  Usage:
    {%- capture wholesale_lock -%}
      {%- render 'wholesale-lock-status', product: card_product -%}
    {%- endcapture -%}
    {%- if wholesale_lock contains 'product-locked' -%} ... {%- endif -%}
  ================================================================
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- liquid
  assign wholesale_locked_handles = 'bracelet,bracelets,earrings,necklace,ready-to-wear,rings' | split: ','

  assign wholesale_is_b2b_customer = false
  if customer and customer.tags contains 'B2B'
    assign wholesale_is_b2b_customer = true
  endif

  if wholesale_is_b2b_customer
    echo 'is-b2b'
  else
    if product != blank
      for wholesale_check_collection in product.collections
        if wholesale_locked_handles contains wholesale_check_collection.handle
          echo ' product-locked'
          break
        endif
      endfor
    endif
    if collection != blank
      if wholesale_locked_handles contains collection.handle
        echo ' collection-locked'
      endif
    endif
  endif
-%}
{%- comment -%}
  When the current product is wholesale-locked for this customer,
  emit CSS that hides the BSS B2B quantity-discount table (rendered
  client-side by the BSS app) and any other volume / bulk pricing
  UI. This style block is small and harmless if emitted multiple
  times on a page (the cascade dedupes it).
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- if product != blank and wholesale_is_b2b_customer == false -%}
  {%- assign _wholesale_emit_hide_css = false -%}
  {%- for wholesale_check_collection in product.collections -%}
    {%- if wholesale_locked_handles contains wholesale_check_collection.handle -%}
      {%- assign _wholesale_emit_hide_css = true -%}
      {%- break -%}
    {%- endif -%}
  {%- endfor -%}
  {%- if _wholesale_emit_hide_css -%}
    <style>
      .bss-b2b-qty-table-wrapper,
      .bss-b2b-cart-item-qty-table,
      .quantity_break_table,
      [bss-b2b-qty-table],
      .volume-pricing,
      .bulk-order-form {
        display: none !important;
      }
    </style>
  {%- endif -%}
{%- endif -%}
